  â€˜DEBUGDEBUGASSERTâ€™ [-Werror=implicit-function-declaration]

Daniel Stenberg (22 May 2017)
- assert: avoid, use DEBUGASSERT instead!
  
  ... as it does extra checks to actually work.
  
  Reported-by: jonrumsey at github
  Fixes #1504

